<div class="hero-section" style=" min-height:800px">
    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
        </div>
        <!-- Whole white box layout -->
        <div class="about-section">

            <!-- Top paragraphs -->
            <div class="about-top-text">
                <p>
                    🎙 Radio Bharati is the exemplary initiative of BVICAM, New Delhi, in the field of broadcasting.
                    It is packed with passion ❤, fueled with various programmes prepared by students, and presents a young style that is energetic and classy.
                </p>
                <p>
                    📻 The station blends information, education, and entertainment for youth and has become the destination station for all listeners.
                </p>

                <p>
                    ✨ Radio Bharati is a unique blend of immediacy, intimacy, and accessibility that makes it a beloved companion for millions of listeners.
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- VIDEO + TEXT Section -->
            <div class="about-video-text-row">

                <div class="about-video">
                    <video controls poster="video-thumbnail.jpg">
                        <source src="your-video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser does not support the video tag.
                    </video>
                </div>
                <div class="about-desc">
                    <h3>🌟Our Vision</h3>
                    <p>
                        To inspire youth with meaningful content and create an accessible
                        digital radio platform.
                    </p>
                    <h3>🎯Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>
                        To promote knowledge, culture, creativity and entertainment through
                        high-quality radio programmes.
                    </p>
                    <h3>🤝Our Commitment</h3>
                    <p>
                        We ensure Radio Bharati remains a vital part of our media landscape
                        for generations to come.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Bottom text -->
            <div class="about-bottom-text">
                <p>
                    🎧 At Radio Bharati, we believe in empowering students with real-time skills, creativity, and teamwork.
                    With modern studio facilities and passionate contributors, we continue to deliver fresh, dynamic content every day.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>